  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House", 
    "date": "2017-07-20T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "STEM to STEAM Act of 2017\n\nThis bill amends the STEM Education Act of 2015 to include: (1) among the purposes for which the National Science Foundation shall award competitive, merit-reviewed grants the support of the integration of art and design in STEM (science, technology, engineering, and mathematics) educational programs; and (2) among activities supported by such grants the design and testing of programming that integrates art and design in STEM education in order to promote creativity and innovation."
  }, 
